metadata.name: THE FRACTALS OF ENYGMA
metadata.description:
An alien element which fell from the sky and fell in to a deep sea which started releasing fractals which made it a Green Sea. These fractals help in healing faster and hence the water of this sea helps in healing humans and animals which is yet to be discovered by the humans.
This is a Fantasy Concept Art - Digital Painting created using Procreate.
Medium- PNG (2048 x 2048)
